Package: NCBI.BLAST2DT
Type: Package
Title: Submit DNA sequences to NCBI BLAST and get hits results in an R data.table.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Yoann",
           family = "Pageaud",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
