           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1392-1744"))
Description: NCBI.BLAST2DT is a R package allowing you to submit DNA sequences to NCBI BLAST servers, to retrieve potential hits on a selected genome or sequence database, and to collect all results within an R data.table.
